summary: Warner Bros. Box Office Expectations for Pokemon Detective Pikachu Revealed!
title: Warner Bros. Box Office Expectations for Pokemon Detective Pikachu Revealed!
body:
Warner Bros. Box Office Expectations for Pokemon Detective Pikachu Revealed!

Pokemon Detective Pikachu is less than a week a way from hitting the box office, and we’ve got Warner Bros.’ box office expectations for the Ryan Reynolds starring flick.

Our source tells us that Pokemon Detective Pikachu is expected to bring in $40 million in its opening weekend and $100 million in its box office run.

Those expectations are significantly lower thanpredictions that have the film…

summary: How can you get Sonic the Hedgehog so wrong when Detective Pikachu is getting it so right
title: How can you get Sonic the Hedgehog so wrong when Detective Pikachu is getting it so right
body:
How can you get Sonic the Hedgehog so wrong when Detective Pikachu is getting it so right - I didn’t care much for the look of Detective Pikachu to start with, now I’m totally behind it. Can’t see it happen again with the Sonic movie

I’ve had this one on the back burner for a while, but with the cataclysmic reaction to the trailer dropping for the upcoming Sonic the Hedgehog movie, it felt an apt time to move this up the schedule and have this conversation now.

Both Sonic the Hedgehog and Detective Pikachu are two movies with a number of notable similarities: They’re both video game adaptations that take their mascot…

In questo nuovo aggiornamento vi proponiamo il poster in versione RealD 3D di Pokémon – Detective Pikachu, il live action dedicato al famoso franchise.

summary: DETECTIVE PIKACHU PLAYMOJI PACK AVAILABLE ON SUPPORTED ANDROID DEVICES
title: DETECTIVE PIKACHU PLAYMOJI PACK AVAILABLE ON SUPPORTED ANDROID DEVICES
body: If you have an Android device that includes an AR Core and can utilize Playground, you can now download a Detective Pikachu Playmoji Pack for some photographic fun. This AR photo experience includes Pikachu, Charizard, Jigglypuff and Mr. Mime, and lets you take pictures with them in the real world.
